{"tid":1144500,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【安心取代】黃心穎孭重飛《牛下女高音》要重拍 傳江嘉敏頂替做女主角","createTime":"2019-05-08T06:11:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T10:13:28.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"132749097b5c7a52fd0ce5705e17ffcb23f0ec9e","tid":1144500,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T06:11:40.000Z","msg":"《安心偷食》的男女主角許志安和黃心穎都分別停工，之前黃心穎拍落的劇集都要易角重拍，其中《法證先鋒IV》由湯洛雯（靚湯）頂替演出，靚湯更被監製梅小青要求減肥10磅。而另一部黃心穎孭重飛的新劇《牛下女高音》，《蘋果》收到消息由江嘉敏頂替重拍。<br />\n現年24歲的大台小花江嘉敏，於16年加入無綫，在劇集《親親我好媽》中扮演江美儀的大女，劇集出街時被網民大讚靚女又有演技，江嘉敏於17歲已經拍戲，曾主演「香港鮮浪潮國際短片競賽最佳創意獎學院組」的得獎作品──《野犬與貓咪》，當中有床戲及被父親侵犯的戲份，演出大膽。<br />\n《牛下女高音》全劇30集，據知黃心穎戲份由頭帶到尾，由於該劇拍完近一年，演員髮型已不一樣，重拍有很多困難。其中有份演出的吳岱融曾表示，重拍唔會埋怨任何人，大家都想做好件事，希望觀眾可以睇到。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190508/large/1557294550_9a28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190508%2Flarge%2F1557294550_9a28.jpg&h=4edd5db9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190508/59576736\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190508%2F59576736&d=6Mci4xO0oquEcg2hov7%2Fciq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=4174ed7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190508%2F59576736&h=59b0ed26\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190508/59576736</a>"},{"pid":"b4fe423e9677438778b33282ce6aac65f425a744","tid":1144500,"uid":228894,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T06:13:06.000Z","msg":"搵隻雞代替另一隻雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f02b500e982b2d14b7ed0a96f62b0fdb1e64d74","tid":1144500,"uid":107364,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T06:16:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},